{"tid":647703,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"香港中學奇趣盃辯論：「雲加對阿仙奴功大於過」結果","createTime":"2018-04-30T05:24:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T17:35:33.000Z","uid":14075,"like":9,"dislike":149,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"b07d735001253b23ad32667b2e2ff85f1ab1c4c7","tid":647703,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T05:24:48.000Z","msg":"根據昨日(4月29日)香港01報道，以趣味辯題聞名的奇趣盃進行第二回合賽事。其中一道題目 : 雲加對阿仙奴功大於過。甲方隊 (功大於過) 清一色男生，來自聖保羅書院 ; 乙方 (過大於功) 則是全女班，來自中華傳道會安柱中學。辯論後，評判裁定乙方得勝。然而，甲方落敗原因卻令人匪夷所思，原因是甲方隊伍為男生，並對女生隊員欠缺風度和太兇。<br />\n<br />\n比賽中，評判認為雙方列舉的論點不鮮明，更指出乙方對足球的認知比甲方低。但關鍵在於，<span style=\"color: red;\">甲方為男校隊伍，又有(認識足球的)先天優勢，更對女性隊員風度不足，令乙方被嚇怕。因為裁定乙方反勝</span>。<br />\n<br />\n結果係女人又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bafcf07b4642e7b3b2de1f458212ff7b06e010d","tid":647703,"uid":30768,"like":78,"dislike":1,"score":77,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T05:26:40.000Z","msg":"裁判=反雲賤畜"},{"pid":"e9e6d0914f30f728b24e2199320c1a37c41dc786","tid":647703,"uid":14075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T05:30:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57ab74eaddca12566edf1f809ba726e523529e77","tid":647703,"uid":55,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T05:31:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3f40ca34e92725f65c0b6ff5b64da78eeb6469f6","tid":647703,"uid":86833,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T05:31:29.000Z","msg":"反雲不得善終"},{"pid":"0f71a27315d7ce0be69c6e0c7d1c13e44253e23c","tid":647703,"uid":38189,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T05:40:01.000Z","msg":"女人撚識波咩屌佢老母，叫佢地講雲加不敗陣容都up唔出啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee22719e01f18c52a2dd2c8227b63ca4c9c312aa","tid":647703,"uid":14075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0f71a27315d7ce0be69c6e0c7d1c13e44253e23c","tid":647703,"uid":38189,"like":42,"dislike":0,"sc